.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: coral, chestnut, azure, grey, blood-red
There are 5 different nationalities: french, nigerian, spanish, argentine, indian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, iced-juice, juice, almond-milk
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: coralmaster, havana, chaman, game, oliveros
5 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, lizard, frog, rabbit
1. the french is the person who likes azure
2. the swedish is the owner of the lizard
3. the nigerian is the person drinking juice
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes grey
5. the person who likes chestnut is the person drinking lemonade
6. the chaman-smoker is the owner of the rat
7. the person who likes blood-red is the havana-smoker
8. the person drinking iced-juice is in the middle
9. the argentine is on the far left
10. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog
11. the owner of the rabbits is on the left or right of the havana-smoker
12. the coralmaster-smoker is the person drinking 7up
13. the spanish is the game-smoker
14. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who likes coral
15. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    blood-red	|     coral	|      azure	|     chestnut	|     grey	|
| Nationality	|   argentine	|    nigerian	|    french	|    spanish	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     hedgehog	|    rabbit	|     rat	|     frog	|      lizard	|
| Beverage	|    almond-milk	|     juice	|     iced-juice	|    lemonade	|      7up	|
| Cigar		|   havana	|    oliveros	|  chaman	|    game	|   coralmaster	|
